---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Methodology | SIR Saathi">
  <main class="shell content-page">
    <h1>Methodology</h1>
    <p>Guidance is based on state registry entries, deterministic rules, and official-source links.</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Record official SIR dates and source links by state.</li>
      <li>Start each state at guidance-only capability.</li>
      <li>Promote search only after parser validation, redaction, and privacy review.</li>
      <li>Show official fallback links for every action.</li>
    </ol>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
